Flow.description: "All standard updates for when changes are made to the Opportunity object (No Recursion) Just Do It! Any actions to always be perfomed on Opportunity updates Notify Billing for Renewal No Changes Send a notice to Billing if a Renewal No Changes is processed Is Type Changed or New? Always set Opportunity Source to equal Opportunity Type to allow for legacy reports and processes New Customer Closed Won No Task? New Customer Closed Won with Task? Create or update a 90 day follow up task for closed business for New Customers Update NRR? Set the NRR value to be the sum of the Total Installation and Total Equipment values. Submit to CSD Trigger? Process remaining steps when the Submit to CSD button sets the Trigger Submit field New Service Reduction? Create a Service Reduction Offset record for newly assigned Service Reduction Opportunities Submit to OSP Triggered? Button/Link triggered process to submit an Opportunity to OSP and create an OSP Project Turn Up Month Change? Send notice if a PM moves large Opp into a different month Out of Rejected? Send a Chatter post to the Service Delivery Manager when an Opportunity transitions out of the Rejected Delivery Stage Entered Closed Lost Reason? Set Opportunity Stage to Cancelled when CSD selects the Cancel button Service Delivery Completed? Send an email to a designated Partner/Customer Delivery Contact when the Delivery Status of the Opportunity changes to Complete. Billing Enable Trigger? Execute this flow when the Billing Enable button sets the Trigger Billing Enable field Billing Enabled? When a Billing Enabled Date and Ticket # has been added to an Opportunity send an email with details to Billing New Project Manager Selected? Check for a CSD Rep being selected and update to Assigned and send out email "
